sentences: His solos often closely toe the line of the main melodic theme, with his outro in 'nobody wey no fit make am' a case in point.
In 2003, Fiokee began studying mechanical engineering at Delta State and began playing at churches.
In 2008, Fiokee went to Lagos State to participate in a reality television music competition show called Star Quest and won as part of a group called Diamonds.
In 2016, Fiokee started a record label called Fiokee Records.
